## Instructions
1. Analyze the performance data to identify which message patterns lead to higher conversion rates.
2. Look for common traits in converted vs non-converted journeys.
3. Identify winning patterns (tone, length, CTA style, personalization, urgency level).
4. Propose specific template rewrites that incorporate the winning patterns.
5. Keep the same template variables/placeholders — only change the copy and structure.

## Rules
